      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The new snow and wind slabs of the last few days are lying on surface hoar in particular on wind-protected shady slopes. Distinct weak layers exist in the old snowpack. This applies in particular on west, north and east facing slopes above the tree line as well as in areas close to the tree line. <br/> <br/> The snowpack will be moist at low altitude. On steep sunny slopes the snowpack will only just freeze."
      },
